ABC's Zahn Bids Adieu: Kathleen Sullivan has been notified that today will be 
her last day as anchor on "CBS This Morning," even though Paula Zahn still has 
not been officially signed as her replacement. Zahn, news anchor on ABC's "Good 
Morning America," said goodby on the air on Thursday. 
</P>
