OWNED CORPORATIONS; USSR -- LABOR; USSR -- ECONOMY; GOVERNMENT REFORM; PRIVATE 
PROPERTY; BUSINESS -- USSR; USSR -- INDUSTRY; USSR -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS; USSR 
-- AGRICULTURE; PROPERTY RIGHTS 
</P>
