(EQUIPMENT); OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY; HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS; HIGH RISE 
BUILDINGS; SAN FRANCISCO -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; BUILDING INDUSTRY -- 
SAN FRANCISCO; SWINERTON &amp; WALBERG CO; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; OCCUPATIONAL 
