<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The NBA has rewarded Commissioner David Stern for helping make it a highly 
successful venture by making him the highest-paid commissioner in pro sports. 
His new five-year contract calls for $27.5 million, including a $10-million 
bonus. 
</P>
<P>
Paul Tagliabue of the NFL is paid $1 million a year, baseball's Fay Vincent 
$500,000 and the NHL's John Ziegler $425,000. 
</P>
</TEXT>
