PUBLIC HEALTH; PUBLIC SAFETY; DOCTORS; PEST CONTROL; HEALTH HAZARDS; 
DEMONSTRATIONS -- ORANGE COUNTY; CALIFORNIA -- SUITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
