continues along Newport Beach shoreline. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, A cleanup worker stacks oil-filled plastic bags so a bulldozer can 
easily load them into a truck later. CHRISTINE WALTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
